<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.3.6">
<l>mallaimā munnī ratarpaṭa malaiyā laṇaiceytu makiḻntavaṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>kalliṉmī tiyaṉṟa kaṭimati ḷilaṅkai kalaṅkavōr vāḷitoṭ ṭāṉai</l>
<l>celvanāṉ maṟaiyōr nāṅkainaṉ ṉaṭuvuḷ cempoṉcey kōyili ṉuḷḷē,</l>
<l>allimā malarāḷ taṉṉoṭu maṭiyēṉ kaṇṭukoṇ ṭallaltīrn tēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, his servant, having seen for myself, within the Cempoṉcey Temple</l>
<l rend="indent">right in the center of Nāṅkai, with experts of the precious four Vedas,</l>
<l>Along with her of the great lotus blossom, the one who rejoiced,</l>
<l rend="indent">having made a dam of boulders,</l>
<l>So a passage appeared in the three waters of the bounteous sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who discharged one arrow</l>
<l>So Lanka with fortified walls which were built on top of a hill, was terrified,</l>
<l rend="indent">I ceased [all] sorrows.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
